    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em data-start=\"742\" data-end=\"774\">6th-level Shadow Lords feature</em></p><p data-start=\"776\" data-end=\"823\">You exploit hesitation with ruthless precision.</p><p data-start=\"825\" data-end=\"1031\">While raging, when a creature within <strong data-start=\"862\" data-end=\"872\">5 feet</strong> of you makes an attack roll <strong data-start=\"901\" data-end=\"922\">with disadvantage</strong>, you may use your <strong data-start=\"941\" data-end=\"953\">reaction</strong> to force the creature to <strong data-start=\"979\" data-end=\"1000\">reroll the attack</strong> and take the <strong data-start=\"1014\" data-end=\"1030\">lower result</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"1033\" data-end=\"1178\">You can use this feature a number of times equal to your <strong data-start=\"1090\" data-end=\"1111\">proficiency bonus</strong>, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a <strong data-start=\"1164\" data-end=\"1177\">long rest</strong>.</p>",
